    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the legendary S54-powered platform, offering the visceral engagement of a 3.2L inline-six with an 8,000 RPM redline. The high-revving power plant features a recently serviced Double-VANOS system for precise valve timing and optimal torque delivery. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and delivered through a limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including the installation of a subframe reinforcement kit to address chassis fatigue and a recent rod bearing service. The suspension geometry remains tight with refreshed trailing arm bushings and dampers, ensuring the neutral handling and communicative steering rack performance expected of the M-division. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the drivetrain and structural integrity make this an exceptional driver's car.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
