    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the ideal balance between performance and value. The exterior presents beautifully with a high-gloss finish, showing only minor, typical signs of road use like small stone chips on the hood. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features well-preserved upholstery with no rips or stains, and all power features, including the ice-cold A/C and premium sound system, operate as they should. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and quiet, benefiting from a recent full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. With a set of high-tread tires and a complete service history included, this car is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
      "price": 31500.0,
